data.description: ** Sellers are offering $3500 in seller concessions! Buy down your rate or use to help make this home yours!! Welcome to this 4 bedroom 3 full bath home in a highly desired neighborhood! You will not be disappointed with the LVP flooring throughout the entire home! Stainless steal appliances in the kitchen with granite countertops and an island for extra counter space! This home has a formal dining area along with enough room for a table in the kitchen area as well! A bedroom on the 1st floor is an added bonus for a guest room or for a study? The list just keeps going! The Master Bedroom is massive and when you check out the master closet, it is literally almost another room and extra space for activities!   The laundry room is located upstairs so you won't have to worry about carrying laundry up and down stairs!!  The back yard is enclosed with a privacy , white vinyl fence and great for entertaining.  The owners have added gutters to the exterior for extra protection to the foundation what it rains!     You don't want to miss this one, Call your agent or me for more information!!
